        "evaluable_by_ia": true
      },
      {
        "id": "pdp_base_legale",
        "label": "Base légale du traitement",
        "status": "oui",
        "quote": "Our legal bases for controlling or processing personal data are:\n\n- **Article 6.1(a) GDPR (Consent):**You provide informed consent to us or have a reasonable expectation that we will use your information in a certain way – for example, to engage in our community discussions, or to hear about new services or offers.\n- **Article 6.1(b) GDPR (Contract):**Providing our services and fulfilling our obligations to you, usually relating to a terms of service or partnership agreement;\n- **Article 6.1(c) GDPR (Legal Obligation):**The necessity to meet compliance with our legal obligations; and/or\n- **Article 6.1(f) GDPR (Legitimate Interest):**Where it is in our legitimate interests to do so.",
        "quote_verified": false,
        "evaluable_by_ia": true
      },
      {
        "id": "pdp_obligatoire",
        "label": "Caractère obligatoire/facultatif + conséquences",
        "status": "oui",
        "quote": "Where we rely on a specific basis for processing your information and you wish to object to that processing, you must be aware that it might not be possible for you to continue using our services.",
